  <brief_title>Prediction of Thyroid Cancer From Ultrasonographic Characteristics of Thyroid Nodules</brief_title>
  <official_title>Evaluation of Thyroid Fine Needle Aspiration Biopsies: Prediction of Thyroid Cancer From Ultrasonographic Characteristics of Thyroid Nodules</official_title>
